  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あなたは神子でしょう？
ならば、神子らしく
品行方正を心がけるべきです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're a Chosen, correct? In which case,
as a Chosen should, you should aim to
have exceptional conduct.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>へへっ、ゼロス怒られてやんの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehe, Zelos is getting scooolded.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>君もだ！神子のそばにいる者として、
勢いで突っ込むのではなく、
品行方正を心がけてくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You, as well! As someone by the
Chosen's side, you shouldn't be
rushing into things with such impulse,
instead aiming to have exceptional conduct.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんな事言うけどさぁ〜。
そっちのお友達も
全然、品行方正じゃないよね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You say that, but... your friend over there
doesn't have exceptional conduct at all, does he?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだよな。
さっき、法なんて守る気ないって
はっきりと言ってたし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's right. Earlier, he said totally clearly
that he has no interest in following the law.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、言ったな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, I did say that, actually.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>くっ、ユーリ、君って奴は……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ack! Yuri, you're so...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
